<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<script src="http://code.jquery.com/jquery-latest.js">
</script>
<script>
$(document).ready(function () {
$("#but1").dblclick(function () {
$("[align]").hide();
});
$("#but2").dblclick(function () {
$("[align]").show();
});
});
</script>
</head>
<body>

<button id="but1">Click me</button>
<button id="but2">Click me for show</button>

<p align="center" >If you double-click the "Click me" button, I disappear. If you double-click the "Click me for show" button, I will show.</p>
<p>Double-click the "Click me" button</p>
<p>Double-click the "Click me for show" button</p>
</body>
</html>
